ruby setup
==========
i am using sass for the css
 * install rvm (ruby version manager) https://rvm.beginrescueend.com/
 * run "bundle install" to get haml and sass
 * start "sass --watch sass/:css/" to convert sass files instant

node setup
==========
follow https://github.com/joyent/node/wiki/Installation to install node
then install npm

   $ curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sh

install via npm

node install jade # template engine
node install socket.io # async channel handling
node install coffee # js on steroids
node install express # rails for node.js
